Overview

  The e-Mail Server Maven Plugin launches an e-mail server during the
  Maven build life-cycle for use in integration tests.
  
* Goals

  The e-Mail Server Maven Plugin has two goals
  
  * {{{./run-mojo.html}emailserver:run}} Launches the configured e-mail server.
  
  * {{{./stop-mojo.html}emailserver:stop}} Shuts down the running e-mail server.

* Usage

  General instructions on how to use the e-Mail Server Maven Plugin can be found
  on the {{{./usage.html}usage page}}.

